<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. فَقِيْدٌ يُبَكِّيْهِ بِلاَطٌ وغَرْقَدُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>ومَسْجِدُهُ فَالمُوحِشَاتُ لِفْقْدِهِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>خَلاَءٌ لَهُ فِيه مَقَامٌ وَمَقْعَدُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَبَكّىْ رَسُوْلَ اللهِ يَا عَيْنُ عَبْرَةً<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَلاَ أعْرِفَنّكَ الدَّهْرَ دَمْعُكِ يَجْمُدُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَمَا لَكِ لاَ تَبْكِيْنَ ذَا النِّعْمَةِ الَّتِيْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>عَلَى النَّاسِ مِنْهَا سَابِغٌ يَتَغَمَّدُ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَجُوْدِيْ عَلَيْهِ بالدُّمُوْعِ وأعْولِي<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>لِفَقْدِ الَّذِي لاَ مِثْلَهُ الدَّهْرُ يُوْجَدُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَمَا فَقَدْ المَاضُوْنَ مِثْلَ مُحَمَّدٍ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَلاَ مِثْلَهُ حَتَّى القِيَامَةَ يُفْقَدُ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>أَعَفَّ وَأَوْفَى ذِمَّةً بَعْدَ ذِمَّةٍ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَأَقْرَبَ مِنْهُ نَائِلاً لاَ يُنَكَّدُ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وأَبْذَلَ مِنْهُ لِلطَّرِيْفِ وتَالِدٍ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>إِذَا ظَنَّ مِعْطَاءٌ بِمَا كَانَ يُتْلَدُ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَأَكْرَمَ حَيّاً فِي البُيُوْتِ إِذَا انْتَمَى<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَأَكْرَمَ جَداً أبْطَحِيّاً يُسَوَّدُ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وأَمْنَعَ ذِرْوَاتٍ وأَثْبَتَ فِي العُلَى<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>دَعَائِمَ عِزٍّ شَاهِقَاتٍ تُشَيَّدُ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وأَثْبَتَ فَرْعاً فِي الفُرُوْعِ ومَثْبَتاً<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وعُوْداً غَذَاهُ المُزْنُ فَالعُوْدُ أَغْيَدُ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>